Sheriff_Woody http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sheriff_Woody 0 Sheriff Woody Pride is the main character and the protagonist in the Toy Story franchise created by Pixar. He is a pullstring cowboy rag doll and one of the two leaders (along with Buzz Lightyear) of the toys in the movies. His facial features are based on Tone Thyne, a former Disney animator. He is voiced by Tom Hanks in the feature-length films and short films, and by Tom's brother Jim Hanks in video games and merchandise.
